00:18:25.122 --> 00:18:26.622
- Okay, thank you.

00:18:27.661 --> 00:18:31.574
There's a good clarification
that's happened here,

00:18:31.574 --> 00:18:34.819
the term of art that you use
is a competency evaluation

00:18:34.819 --> 00:18:36.995
is competency to stand trial

00:18:36.995 --> 00:18:39.079
and conservatorship evaluation

00:18:39.079 --> 00:18:40.947
is a conservatorship evaluation.

00:18:40.947 --> 00:18:42.383
All right, then let me change my language

00:18:42.383 --> 00:18:46.550
because I'm talking about a
conservatorship evaluation.

00:18:47.858 --> 00:18:50.499
The tools that I've usually seen

00:18:50.499 --> 00:18:53.626
and that the courts have usually requested

00:18:53.626 --> 00:18:56.709
are what you were saying of IQ exams,

00:18:58.601 --> 00:19:01.789
various short term memory tests,

00:19:01.789 --> 00:19:04.547
problem solving skills, et cetera.

00:19:04.547 --> 00:19:07.464
They're usually tools that are done

00:19:08.493 --> 00:19:12.801
in a relatively artificial
context in an office.

00:19:12.801 --> 00:19:16.699
They're usually done without any support,

00:19:16.699 --> 00:19:19.030
even if the person
generally does have support

00:19:19.030 --> 00:19:20.697
in their daily life.

00:19:23.102 --> 00:19:26.102
They aren't done with what decisions

00:19:27.816 --> 00:19:31.483
an individual make
actually make day to day.

00:19:32.785 --> 00:19:35.452
From our perspective as lawyers,

00:19:36.860 --> 00:19:39.027
the ideal process would be

00:19:40.904 --> 00:19:45.071
spending real time from dawn
to dusk with an individual,

00:19:46.722 --> 00:19:49.781
walking with them through their life,

00:19:49.781 --> 00:19:54.275
seeing at what points
they act independently,

00:19:54.275 --> 00:19:57.119
at what points they act with support,

00:19:57.119 --> 00:20:00.550
and at other points
someone else is intervening

00:20:00.550 --> 00:20:04.048
because they are unable
to make a decision.

00:20:04.048 --> 00:20:07.825
That would be something that
happens over a week or two.

00:20:07.825 --> 00:20:10.408
Obviously the ideal approach is

00:20:11.379 --> 00:20:15.251
administratively and
financially unfeasible.

00:20:15.251 --> 00:20:18.976
That's not something we
can ask you to implement.

00:20:18.976 --> 00:20:20.726
Was there a question?

