00:31:12.747 --> 00:31:14.628
there is no recourse.

00:31:14.628 --> 00:31:16.160
There's no recourse.

00:31:16.160 --> 00:31:19.077
Legally, that person is essentially

00:31:22.633 --> 00:31:26.133
at the whim and mercy of the conservator.

